full_title: MILLION DOLLAR BABY by Tommy Richman
title: MILLION DOLLAR BABY

description.plain:
“Million Dollar Baby” is the breakout single from Woodbridge, Virginia native Tommy Richman. The song serves as the lead single for Richman’s upcoming album, Coyote. The song was released on April 26th, 2024. It debuted and peaked at #2 on the Billboard Hot 100 on the chart dated May 11th.

The song quickly went viral on Tiktok where it became the soundtrack to multiple video trends including a dance challenge. This led to “Million Dollar Baby” becoming the longest-running #1 song on the Tiktok Billboard Top 50 with a 10 week run that lasted from May to July of 2024.

This song uses funk and R&B elements to create a very unique production style with vocal layering, staccato synth lines, and trap percussion. Lyrically, the song discusses Richman’s desire to make it in the industry and represent his home state of Virginia. He also talks about the importance of staying out of trouble on the way to achieving your goals and knowing what you’re worth.
